where people have written some stuff at the top and some stuff at the bottom, which actually

00:11:11.460 --> 00:11:14.900
brings me to my next poll.

00:11:14.900 --> 00:11:17.219
I'll come out to that in just a second.

00:11:17.219 --> 00:11:23.340
And so Read Excel is really focused on helping you find or identify this data rectangle and

00:11:23.340 --> 00:11:25.059
bringing just that data rectangle in.

00:11:25.059 --> 00:11:28.900
So that's indicated by this yellow box.

00:11:28.900 --> 00:11:34.900
So Read Excel is highly focused on a data rectangle as opposed to absorbing an entire

00:11:34.900 --> 00:11:37.219
spreadsheet in all of its glory.

00:11:37.219 --> 00:11:43.219
So this would be a good time to launch the second poll of three.

